tyle=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">9)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">10&ordm; - Pr&ecirc;mio &ndash; 1 Ventilador</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Par&aacute;grafo Primeiro - Cada servidor filiado ter&aacute; direito a um cupom que dever&aacute; ser adquirido gratuitamente na sede do Sindicato preenchido e depositado em urna no pr&oacute;prio sindicato.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Par&aacute;grafo Segundo - Os cupons de sorteio n&atilde;o dever&atilde;o ser entregues &agrave; terceiros, somente ao servidor que dever&aacute; assinar comprovante de retirada do cupom.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Par&aacute;grafo Terceiro - O Mesmo cupom dar&aacute; direito ao servidor de concorrer a todos os brindes listados acima. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Par&aacute;grafo Quarto - Aquele que for sorteado com algum pr&ecirc;mio n&atilde;o poder&aacute; concorrer aos demais pr&ecirc;mios. (Os pr&ecirc;mios n&atilde;o ser&atilde;o cumulativos)</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">DA DATA DO SORTEIO E DO RESULTADO</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Art. 5&ordm; - Os cupons dever&atilde;o ser adquiridos pelos associados na sede do sindicato na seguinte data: 18/04/17 &agrave; 27/04/2017.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Art.5&ordm; - O sorteio ser&aacute; realizado dia 28 de abril de 2017 a partir das 19 horas na Pra&ccedil;a C&iacute;vica.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Par&aacute;grafo Primeiro &ndash; Os sorteados ser&atilde;o aqueles cujo cupom for retirado da urna no ato do sorteio, onde dever&aacute; constar o n&uacute;mero do cupom o nome do servidor o telefone e local de trabalho. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Par&aacute;grafo Segundo &ndash; O resultado final do sorteio ser&aacute; divulgado no site do sindicato <a href=\"../../../\">www.sindceres.com.br</a>, &nbsp;bem como por meio de carta, jornal e revista de vincula&ccedil;&atilde;o pr&oacute;pria da categoria.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Par&aacute;grafo Terceiro &ndash; O servidor sorteado ser&aacute; informado por meio de telefonema, e-mail ou outro meio id&ocirc;neo.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">DA ENTREGA DA PREMIA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Artigo 6&ordm; - A entrega da premia&ccedil;&atilde;o ser&aacute; no mesmo evento na pra&ccedil;a c&iacute;vica para os sorteados presentes. Os sorteados que n&atilde;o estivem presentes ter&atilde;o o prazo de 30 dias a partir da data do sorteio para buscar o pr&ecirc;mio na sede do sindicato.</span> <span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;N&atilde;o haver&aacute; a necessidade da presen&ccedil;a do contemplado no momento do sorteio, tendo em vista que a lista dos sorteados ser&aacute; divulgada pelo Sindicato.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Artigo 7&ordm; - Caso o Pr&ecirc;mio n&atilde;o seja reclamado e o servidor n&atilde;o seja encontrado o mesmo perder&aacute; o direito ao pr&ecirc;mio.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR;\">Artigo 8&ordm; - Somente o servidor ganhador do Pr&ecirc;mio poder&aacute; recebe-lo lo. Seja no ato do sorteio seja na sede do sindicato.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">9&ordm; - Os sorteados que n&atilde;o preencherem os requisitos do presente regulamento ser&atilde;o automaticamente vetados e exclu&iacute;dos. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">Par&aacute;grafo Primeiro - Todos os participantes, desde j&aacute;, autorizam o Sindicato a utilizar suas imagens e nomes para a divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o dos eventos em quest&atilde;o. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span st